  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini UP</strong> is a free, simple parkour game. Just run and jump while trying to optimize every second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is ideal for players who enjoy challenging themselves, honing their skills, and having some fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini UP <strong>is a solo indie project developed</strong> as part of my early journey in game development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370650/extras/a10102ced195daeafe0155d8bd47a197.avif?t=1774180156\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its main features are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short, adjustable levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100% free</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini UP</strong> includes optional cosmetic skins <strong>that do not affect gameplay.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini UP</strong> is a free, simple parkour game. Just run and jump while trying to optimize every second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is ideal for players who enjoy challenging themselves, honing their skills, and having some fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini UP <strong>is a solo indie project developed</strong> as part of my early journey in game development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4370650/extras/a10102ced195daeafe0155d8bd47a197.avif?t=1774180156\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its main features are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short, adjustable levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100% free</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini UP</strong> includes optional cosmetic skins <strong>that do not affect gameplay.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
